missingdata

Source: vignettes/missingdata.Rmd
missingdata.Rmd
library(greed)

epsi = 0.05
N=100
mu = (diag(3)*(1-epsi)) + (matrix(1,3,3)-diag(3))*epsi

Kh = rep(0,100)
NMIh = rep(0,100)
for (isim in 1:100){
  sbm = rsbm(N,c(1/3,1/3,1/3),mu)
  X=as.matrix(sbm$x)
  ijl = which(X==1,arr.ind = TRUE)
  p1=0.15
  obs1 = rbinom(nrow(ijl),1,rep(p1,nrow(ijl)))
  X[ijl[obs1==0,]]=NA
  ijl = which(X==0,arr.ind = TRUE)
  p0=0.15
  obs0 =rbinom(nrow(ijl),1,rep(p0,nrow(ijl)))
  X[ijl[obs0==0,]]=NA
  Xc = array(0,c(N,N,3))
  Xs=matrix(0,N,N)
  Xs[X==1]=1
  Xc[,,1]=Xs
  Xs=matrix(0,N,N)
  Xs[X==0]=1
  Xc[,,2]=Xs
  Xs=matrix(0,N,N)
  Xs[is.na(X)]=1
  Xc[,,3]=Xs
  sol=greed(Xc)
  Kh[isim]=sol@K
  NMIh[isim]=NMI(sbm$cl,sol@cl)
}
